Turkey Will Build Hospital Complexes in Istanbul, Star Reports

-- B y   M a r k   B e n t l e y
-- 
2011-04-25T05:42:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-25/turkey-will-build-hospital-complexes-in-istanbul-star-reports.html
Turkey  will build two giant
hospital complexes on the Asian and European sides of Istanbul,
Star said citing Prime Minister  Recep Tayyip Erdogan .  The size of the two facilities will total 1.5 million
square meters, Erdogan said in the city yesterday, according to
the newspaper. The land for the complex on the European side has
already been set aside, he said.  Auctions to build the hospitals are about to be held,
Erdogan said, Star reported.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
